    <header>
        <h1>Chronic Diseases</h1>
        <p>Learn about long-term health conditions, their causes, symptoms, prevention, and treatment.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="disease-card">
            <img src="/img/en/5_1.jpg" alt="Cancer">
            <h2>Cancer</h2>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> A disease where abnormal cells grow uncontrollably, affecting various organs.</p>
            <p><strong>Causes:</strong> Genetic mutations, smoking, radiation exposure.</p>
            <p><strong>Symptoms:</strong> Weight loss, lumps, prolonged pain, fatigue.</p>
            <p><strong>Prevention:</strong> Avoid smoking, healthy diet, regular screenings.</p>
            <p><strong>Treatment:</strong> Surgery, chemotherapy, radiation therapy.</p>
        </div>        
        <div class="disease-card">
            <img src="/img/en/5_2.jpg" alt="Heart Disease">
            <h2>Heart Disease</h2>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> A group of conditions affecting heart function.</p>
            <p><strong>Causes:</strong> High cholesterol, high BP, obesity, smoking.</p>
            <p><strong>Symptoms:</strong> Chest pain, shortness of breath, fatigue.</p>
            <p><strong>Prevention:</strong> Heart-healthy diet, exercise, no smoking.</p>
            <p><strong>Treatment:</strong> Medications, lifestyle changes, surgery.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="disease-card">
            <img src="/img/en/5_3.jpg" alt="Diabetes">
            <h2>Diabetes</h2>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> A chronic disease where blood sugar remains high.</p>
            <p><strong>Causes:</strong> Genetics, obesity, lack of exercise, diet.</p>
            <p><strong>Symptoms:</strong> Increased thirst, frequent urination, fatigue.</p>
            <p><strong>Prevention:</strong> Healthy diet, regular exercise, weight control.</p>
            <p><strong>Treatment:</strong> Insulin therapy, medications, lifestyle changes.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
